@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ============== Relationships ==============

### _embed: include children resources
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?_embed=comments

### _embed: include children for a single post
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/1?_embed=comments

### _expand: include parent resource
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments?_expand=post

### _expand: include parent for a single comment
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/1?_expand=post

### Nested resources: get comments of a post
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/1/comments

### Nested resources: create a comment under a post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "new comment via nested route",
  "author": { "name": "oswin", "email": "oswin@example.com" }
}
